---
title: Easy Cottage Beyond Meat® Pie with Cheesy Cheddar Mashed Potatoes
description: This classic casserole combines saucy filling with extra cheesy cheddar mashed potatoes. Broiling for the last few minutes gives this cottage pie a delicious golden crust.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pate-chinois-au-beyond-meat-et-aux-petits-pois-109c371e.jpg
